    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "collate_text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 318,
      "width": 790,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "collate_fn — 从单样本到 batch 的完整变换链\n\n1. crop_and_resize(img)    → (target_H, target_W, 3) e.g. (360, 640, 3)\n2. intrinsic 缩放           → fx,fy,cx,cy 按 resize 比例调整\n3. ego_filter              → |x|>3 & |y|>3 过滤自车点, pc: (N', 3)\n4. range_filter            → xbound/ybound/zbound 裁剪, pc: (N'', 3)\n5. perturbation → init_T   → gt_T + noise (truncated_normal), init_T: (4,4)\n6. color_jitter (optional)  → brightness/contrast/saturation ×0.3\n7. pc_jitter/dropout (opt)  → Gaussian noise / random drop\n8. PC padding + mask       → batch 内 pad 到 max_N, mask: (B, max_N)\n9. to_tensor + to_device   → img: (B,3,H,W)  pc: (B,N,3)  T: (B,4,4)\n\n关键: ego_filter + range_filter 直接影响点云利用率; PC padding 用 mask 确保 padding 点不参与计算",
      "originalText": "collate_fn — 从单样本到 batch 的完整变换链\n\n1. crop_and_resize(img)    → (target_H, target_W, 3) e.g. (360, 640, 3)\n2. intrinsic 缩放           → fx,fy,cx,cy 按 resize 比例调整\n3. ego_filter              → |x|>3 & |y|>3 过滤自车点, pc: (N', 3)\n4. range_filter            → xbound/ybound/zbound 裁剪, pc: (N'', 3)\n5. perturbation → init_T   → gt_T + noise (truncated_normal), init_T: (4,4)\n6. color_jitter (optional)  → brightness/contrast/saturation ×0.3\n7. pc_jitter/dropout (opt)  → Gaussian noise / random drop\n8. PC padding + mask       → batch 内 pad 到 max_N, mask: (B, max_N)\n9. to_tensor + to_device   → img: (B,3,H,W)  pc: (B,N,3)  T: (B,4,4)\n\n关键: ego_filter + range_filter 直接影响点云利用率; PC padding 用 mask 确保 padding 点不参与计算",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 630005,
