    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "img_branch_df_t",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 588,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 175,
      "text": "Image Branch (Cam2BEV) — Tensor Shape 变换\n\n1. SwinT-Tiny (预训练)     (B,3,H,W) → multi-scale features\n2. FPN 多尺度融合           → (B, 1, 256, H/8, W/8)  e.g. (B,1,256,45,80)\n3. LSS 深度估计 (D=89)     → (B, 1, 128, 89, H/8, W/8)\n4. Frustum 几何变换         → 3D frustum points in ego frame [依赖 init_T!]\n5. BEV Pool [CUDA]         → (B, C×nZ, nX, nY)  e.g. (B, 128, 100, 100)\n6. ProjectionHead           → (B, 128, 100, 100)\n\n⚠ init_T 敏感性: Step 4 使用 init_T 逆矩阵投影\n  当 init_T 偏差 >5° 时, BEV 特征严重错位\n  这是大扰动场景下精度下降的根本原因",
      "originalText": "Image Branch (Cam2BEV) — Tensor Shape 变换\n\n1. SwinT-Tiny (预训练)     (B,3,H,W) → multi-scale features\n2. FPN 多尺度融合           → (B, 1, 256, H/8, W/8)  e.g. (B,1,256,45,80)\n3. LSS 深度估计 (D=89)     → (B, 1, 128, 89, H/8, W/8)\n4. Frustum 几何变换         → 3D frustum points in ego frame [依赖 init_T!]\n5. BEV Pool [CUDA]         → (B, C×nZ, nX, nY)  e.g. (B, 128, 100, 100)\n6. ProjectionHead           → (B, 128, 100, 100)\n\n⚠ init_T 敏感性: Step 4 使用 init_T 逆矩阵投影\n  当 init_T 偏差 >5° 时, BEV 特征严重错位\n  这是大扰动场景下精度下降的根本原因",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
