    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "pc_branch_df_t",
      "x": 670,
      "y": 588,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "PC Branch (Lidar2BEV) — Tensor Shape 变换\n\n1. PointToVoxel (spconv)    (B,N,3) → SparseConvTensor, max 120k voxels\n2. SparseEncoder Layer 1    → 16 channels (SparseBasicBlock)\n3. SparseEncoder Layer 2    → 32 channels (下采样 + 残差)\n4. SparseEncoder Layer 3    → 64 channels\n5. SparseEncoder Layer 4    → 128 channels\n6. Z 压缩 + dense()         → (B, C×Z, nX, nY)\n7. ProjectionHead           → (B, 128, 100, 100)\n\n✓ 稳定锚点: 不依赖任何标定参数\n  点云直接在 LiDAR 坐标系体素化\n  无论 init_T 偏差多大, BEV 特征始终稳定",
      "originalText": "PC Branch (Lidar2BEV) — Tensor Shape 变换\n\n1. PointToVoxel (spconv)    (B,N,3) → SparseConvTensor, max 120k voxels\n2. SparseEncoder Layer 1    → 16 channels (SparseBasicBlock)\n3. SparseEncoder Layer 2    → 32 channels (下采样 + 残差)\n4. SparseEncoder Layer 3    → 64 channels\n5. SparseEncoder Layer 4    → 128 channels\n6. Z 压缩 + dense()         → (B, C×Z, nX, nY)\n7. ProjectionHead           → (B, 128, 100, 100)\n\n✓ 稳定锚点: 不依赖任何标定参数\n  点云直接在 LiDAR 坐标系体素化\n  无论 init_T 偏差多大, BEV 特征始终稳定",
      "fontSize": 11,
