    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "fusion_df_t",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 858,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 161,
      "text": "Fusion → Transformer → Prediction Heads — 完整变换链\n\n1. ConvFuser: concat(img_bev, pc_bev)  (B,128,100,100) + (B,128,100,100) → (B,256,100,100) → Conv1x1 → BN → ReLU → (B,embed_dim,H,W)\n2. + pose_embed (可学习)               (B,embed_dim,H,W) + (1,embed_dim,H,W)\n3. Deformable Transformer × L layers   DeformableAttention + MLP + DropPath(0.1) → (B,embed_dim,H,W)\n4. Global Mean Pool                    (B,embed_dim,H,W) → (B,embed_dim)\n5. head_dropout(0.1)                   (B,embed_dim) → (B,embed_dim)\n6. Translation Head: Linear(dim→3)     → ΔT ∈ ℝ³ (B,3)\n7. Rotation Head: Linear(dim→4)        → Δq ∈ ℝ⁴ (B,4) quaternion\n8. get_T_matrix(): quat→mat + tvec→mat → pred_T (B,4,4) SE(3)\n9. 校正: T_gt = T_pred⁻¹ · T_init     → calibrated_T (B,4,4)",
      "originalText": "Fusion → Transformer → Prediction Heads — 完整变换链\n\n1. ConvFuser: concat(img_bev, pc_bev)  (B,128,100,100) + (B,128,100,100) → (B,256,100,100) → Conv1x1 → BN → ReLU → (B,embed_dim,H,W)\n2. + pose_embed (可学习)               (B,embed_dim,H,W) + (1,embed_dim,H,W)\n3. Deformable Transformer × L layers   DeformableAttention + MLP + DropPath(0.1) → (B,embed_dim,H,W)\n4. Global Mean Pool                    (B,embed_dim,H,W) → (B,embed_dim)\n5. head_dropout(0.1)                   (B,embed_dim) → (B,embed_dim)\n6. Translation Head: Linear(dim→3)     → ΔT ∈ ℝ³ (B,3)\n7. Rotation Head: Linear(dim→4)        → Δq ∈ ℝ⁴ (B,4) quaternion\n8. get_T_matrix(): quat→mat + tvec→mat → pred_T (B,4,4) SE(3)\n9. 校正: T_gt = T_pred⁻¹ · T_init     → calibrated_T (B,4,4)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
