    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "loss_df_t",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1110,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 161,
      "text": "Loss Computation Data Flow\n\ntotal_loss =\n  1.0 × translation_loss (SmoothL1)\n  + 0.5 × rotation_loss (四元数测地距离)\n  + 0.5 × PC_reproj_loss (3D 重投影一致性)\n  + 0.5 × quat_norm_loss (单位四元数约束)\n  + 0.3 × axis_loss (Roll×3 + Pitch×1.5 + Yaw×1)\n  + tail_penalty (mean(topk(errors, 10%)) × 2.0)\n\n反向传播: loss → scaler → backward → Heads → TR → Fuser → 双分支",
      "originalText": "Loss Computation Data Flow\n\ntotal_loss =\n  1.0 × translation_loss (SmoothL1)\n  + 0.5 × rotation_loss (四元数测地距离)\n  + 0.5 × PC_reproj_loss (3D 重投影一致性)\n  + 0.5 × quat_norm_loss (单位四元数约束)\n  + 0.3 × axis_loss (Roll×3 + Pitch×1.5 + Yaw×1)\n  + tail_penalty (mean(topk(errors, 10%)) × 2.0)\n\n反向传播: loss → scaler → backward → Heads → TR → Fuser → 双分支",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
