    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eval_df_t",
      "x": 670,
      "y": 1110,
      "width": 580,
      "height": 161,
      "text": "Evaluation Data Flow\n\npred_T (B,4,4) + gt_T (B,4,4)\n→ error_T = gt_T⁻¹ · pred_T\n→ R = error_T[:3,:3], t = error_T[:3,3]\n→ euler = R → (roll, pitch, yaw) in degrees\n→ physical = t → (fwd, lat, ht) in meters\n\n输出 8 维物理误差:\n  旋转: roll(°), pitch(°), yaw(°), rot_error(°)\n  平移: fwd(m), lat(m), ht(m), trans_error(m)",
      "originalText": "Evaluation Data Flow\n\npred_T (B,4,4) + gt_T (B,4,4)\n→ error_T = gt_T⁻¹ · pred_T\n→ R = error_T[:3,:3], t = error_T[:3,3]\n→ euler = R → (roll, pitch, yaw) in degrees\n→ physical = t → (fwd, lat, ht) in meters\n\n输出 8 维物理误差:\n  旋转: roll(°), pitch(°), yaw(°), rot_error(°)\n  平移: fwd(m), lat(m), ht(m), trans_error(m)",
      "fontSize": 11,
