    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "summary_text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1362,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "Image: (B,3,360,640) → SwinT → FPN → (B,1,256,45,80) → LSS → (B,1,128,89,45,80) → Frustum → BEV Pool → (B,C×nZ,100,100) → ProjHead → (B,128,100,100)\nPC:    (B,N,3) → Voxel → SparseConvTensor → Sparse3D (16→32→64→128) → Z compress → (B,C×Z,nX,nY) → ProjHead → (B,128,100,100)\nFuse:  concat → (B,256,100,100) → Conv1x1 → (B,128,100,100) → +pose_embed → TR × L → mean_pool → (B,128) → Heads → (B,3)+(B,4) → get_T → (B,4,4)\n\nTotal: 磁盘 → collate_fn → GPU → 双分支 BEV(128,100,100) → concat(256) → Conv(128) → TR → pool(128) → Linear(3+4) → SE(3)(4,4)",
      "originalText": "Image: (B,3,360,640) → SwinT → FPN → (B,1,256,45,80) → LSS → (B,1,128,89,45,80) → Frustum → BEV Pool → (B,C×nZ,100,100) → ProjHead → (B,128,100,100)\nPC:    (B,N,3) → Voxel → SparseConvTensor → Sparse3D (16→32→64→128) → Z compress → (B,C×Z,nX,nY) → ProjHead → (B,128,100,100)\nFuse:  concat → (B,256,100,100) → Conv1x1 → (B,128,100,100) → +pose_embed → TR × L → mean_pool → (B,128) → Heads → (B,3)+(B,4) → get_T → (B,4,4)\n\nTotal: 磁盘 → collate_fn → GPU → 双分支 BEV(128,100,100) → concat(256) → Conv(128) → TR → pool(128) → Linear(3+4) → SE(3)(4,4)",
      "fontSize": 11,
